{"tid":389867,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"廣角旅行隨身機之選 (rx100, x70, GR...?)","createTime":"2017-09-06T15:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T08:10:00.000Z","uid":50196,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6419e3027a1d19a3a9e22132e3a93c0bca9b80b7","tid":389867,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"小弟去旅行會用A7長插55.8<br />\n搭支手動鏡minolta mc 28 2.8<br />\n但下下換鏡覺得好煩(已經買左個鏡頭套, 掛左喺背囊&quot;咩&quot;帶度, 方便換)<br />\n有時索性用手機snap算<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家考慮買部dc仔, 有廣角焦段 (21-28mm都ok)<br />\n黎取代要換鏡 (會繼續用A7+55.8)<br />\n<br />\n扒文睇過呢幾部<br />\n<br />\nrx100 (iii / iv / v) <br />\n因為主要用廣角焦段, zoom lens好似有啲浪費<br />\n但同樣係sony, 執相執色後製方便啲, 易啲同一發色<br />\n<br />\nGR (i / ii) <br />\n操控性強 多filter玩<br />\n但其實我會執相 所以未有太大興趣<br />\n雖然扒過文 個高對比黑白 後製好難執到gr陣味<br />\n<br />\nx70 <br />\n富士發色<br />\n但機身大舊又重, 又要用鏡頭蓋<br />\n<br />\n想問下有無巴絲會長插55.8, 搭部機仔去旅行?<br />\n你地又會用邊部?<br />\n除左上面幾部, 有無咩其他選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f74dc6fecf672d5939cf85ab6e5020c56fed81e","tid":389867,"uid":50502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"IPHONE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n帶兩部 一機一鏡會唔會有D ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b8a8a7a1ca264afc4e7a8f4c29d1299cb8511d","tid":389867,"uid":38569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"已經有部大機 一定係配GR<br />\n單手操作 放衫袋褲袋都得 又有APSC Sensor"},{"pid":"97a1d1b44bff1a8a62113ceea662f033ffa96be2","tid":389867,"uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經有部大機 一定係配GR<br />\n單手操作 放衫袋褲袋都得 又有APSC Sensor</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無用gr?"},{"pid":"2957abfa12a30135ccb3f934e92a50f58accd5b1","tid":389867,"uid":99209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"x70用家<br />\n放唔到落褲袋，厚，重就唔係好重既<br />\n個電子crop其實唔好用，都係zoom好好多<br />\n不過用過其他兩部都覺佢d色係幾靚<br />\n單手操控無乜問題，拍片個button好難襟<br />\n又有得set唔同自訂mode，方便即係轉，唔洗慢慢手動再較。"},{"pid":"5f0b31869f9d50b867d73c0fe5800933ac74f3fe","tid":389867,"uid":80866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"有同樣困難，留名睇建議"},{"pid":"8310c23e4b45586b07bda4e46d9f57acada523a0","tid":389867,"uid":38569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已經有部大機 一定係配GR<br />\n單手操作 放衫袋褲袋都得 又有APSC Sensor</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無用gr?</blockquote><br />\nGR1同2都用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRX100 iii都用過<br />\n去旅行嗰陣GR做副機係好方便<br />\n不過睇你用唔用得慣個焦段啦"},{"pid":"30d64cedde2d77d079d7bb396741135e669a1046","tid":389867,"uid":12626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:53:47.000Z","msg":"睇你著唔著緊1&quot; vs APSC<br />\n我上年拎RX100M3去歐遊感覺好爽<br />\n<br />\n利申: <br />\n手上仲有X70, 但冇viewfinder感覺係差啲<br />\n同埋去旅行始終都係zoom鏡有著數<br />\n當然睇下你對攝影眼係點"},{"pid":"f7615cd5d1754eeec0406ad9bd7e8d15ac67953c","tid":389867,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:25:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88dbd720a6c751767632b66ddc48fdb12ca5433a","tid":389867,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"Canon g7x mark ii"},{"pid":"4674b84aa90091795309082c784e860710e14a48","tid":389867,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T03:17:36.000Z","msg":"rx0"},{"pid":"57202d2b80d801cc962f24bd973440d2b7464fab","tid":389867,"uid":42624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:11:39.000Z","msg":"GR"},{"pid":"4c05e4582ab92ad6aa80fac820bed33c6bee7e1d","tid":389867,"uid":6071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:16:18.000Z","msg":"我就揀左rx100iv 不過成日覺得擺係褲袋好唔安全 所以就買左條掛頸繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"